1. *Večeri* su bile vrlo neobične. (The evenings were very unusual.)
2. Njegove *večeri* su bile veoma duhovite. (His evenings were very witty.)
3. Uživali smo u *večeri* zajedno. (We enjoyed the evening together.)
4. Ona često provodi *večeri* uz knjigu. (She often spends evenings with a book.)
5. Oni su provodili *večeri* na terasi. (They spent the evenings on the terrace.)
6. Dođite u *večeri* da se družimo. (Come in the evening to hang out.)